{"tid":284431,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梅林牌午餐肉含殘餘獸藥 有腸仔含鈉高標示560倍","createTime":"2017-06-15T02:17:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-15T02:51:08.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"68a926f73728bcd09695e756cea868ed31166b62","tid":284431,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T02:17:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170615/large/1497492485_74a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170615%2Flarge%2F1497492485_74a3.jpg&h=b84c6a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n午餐肉、腸仔等加工肉類食品，雖然自2015年被世界衞生組織歸類為第1組致癌物，但仍屬不少港人日常飲食選擇。消委會今日公佈相關報告，測試25款午餐肉及8款罐裝或瓶裝腸仔樣本，調查發現大部分樣本均屬高鈉、高脂肪，恐有損健康。當中梅林優質午餐肉（昌輝）被驗出含有屬於抗生素類獸藥殘餘，另有1款腸仔樣本的鈉含量比所標示的高出560多倍，而相關個案已交食物安全中心跟進。<br />\n<br />\n是次測試項目包括抗生素、亞硝酸鈉和鈉含量等， 並有檢視樣本的營養標籤，而所有樣本中未有檢出重金屬、乙類促效劑、激素和污染物苯並[a]芘(benzo(a)pyrene)。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56830347&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170615\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56830347%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170615&d=z9kzH8MKTQWsgj0QUwzsjC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=88c843ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56830347%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170615&h=144f8d7f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56830347&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170615</a>"},{"pid":"75281b557984d4b4a58ebe1230f8b67211b8362d","tid":284431,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T02:20:15.000Z","msg":"支那製造"},{"pid":"34e436d4dc8b28656ccaeca0df21f3058ba0b4c0","tid":284431,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T02:21:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10a38adfa99a96c5a5746b645c1907d760c09353","tid":284431,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T02:21:44.000Z","msg":"加工肉類罐頭食品，含高鈉、高脂肪係常識吧 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bab99f7cb01afec36af5fc0d98c65e9563903f1","tid":284431,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T02:23:41.000Z","msg":"鬼叫你窮咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"982490f053157e6746524a6bcc2d6c01d0cfc36a","tid":284431,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T02:25:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支那製造</blockquote><br />\n三花, 泡菜牌牛餐肉唔好得好多<br />\n只係呢隻支那牌子行內連狗都唔屌"},{"pid":"6ea603c6f051f126942ced56372acddaad50df7e","tid":284431,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T02:26:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>支那製造</blockquote><br />\n三花, 泡菜牌牛餐肉唔好得好多<br />\n只係呢隻支那牌子行內連狗都唔屌</blockquote><br />\n加工罐頭肉實係咁架啦<br />\n行內睇你咩行啦 茶記理撚得你咩 最緊要平"},{"pid":"aba028bb358ceab9284b947154528183d82468b4","tid":284431,"uid":108305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T02:26:58.000Z","msg":"起碼都金妹啦 午餐肉就荷美爾最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97a1f0bfa244ce6cc08abd741bf7d65f2a562b57","tid":284431,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T02:27:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>起碼都金妹啦 午餐肉就荷美爾最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n荷美爾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dcdafda64f56d343f08a64a553f532eebc7dd37","tid":284431,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T02:30:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>支那製造</blockquote><br />\n三花, 泡菜牌牛餐肉唔好得好多<br />\n只係呢隻支那牌子行內連狗都唔屌</blockquote><br />\n加工罐頭肉實係咁架啦<br />\n行內睇你咩行啦 茶記理撚得你咩 最緊要平</blockquote><br />\n茶記d牛餐肉邊有咁細罐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4976216e4c2d1a8ef17e556059dff9964ef4231","tid":284431,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T02:32:32.000Z","msg":"唔食囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53543a55e639f188b683d0ddd64834a06291e64a","tid":284431,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T02:32:53.000Z","msg":"食開梅林牌黑白招紙嗰隻&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1799522cba05a0a556b9b381912cd4352ecdef3","tid":284431,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T02:34:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>起碼都金妹啦 午餐肉就荷美爾最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n荷美爾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買開荷美爾 但偏咸"},{"pid":"ee090d478510a0c65b6a0531781716775ee2a4f9","tid":284431,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T02:35:06.000Z","msg":"屌消委會好心做埋 五香肉丁啦屌 同雞肉腸"},{"pid":"f2fd52b226997d03ceba27ae1f09a37a23e2aa35","tid":284431,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T02:36:33.000Z","msg":"消委會：1款梅林午餐肉含獸藥　759樣本最鹹<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/15/103547_ba95e4ae7bbfaa60b18972d4158cbe20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F15%2F103547_ba95e4ae7bbfaa60b18972d4158cbe20.jpg&h=a717fa97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港人喜愛午餐肉和腸仔等加工類罐頭，卻忽略了內含的高鈉和高脂可能引發的健康危機。消委會去年11月至12月期間從香港各大超級市場及糧食店搜集25款午餐肉樣本及8款罐裝或瓶裝腸仔樣本，測試發現其中一款「梅林」優質午餐肉(昌輝)樣本含獸藥殘留抗生素磺胺二甲嘧啶，含量達每公斤199.3微克。該磺胺二甲嘧啶常用於治療患有萎縮性鼻炎的豬隻，若人體進食後，會增加人體內抗藥性存活的風險，當中會有約3%至6%的人對磺胺二甲嘧啶過敏，會導致面部、口腔和舌頭出現皮疹和腫脹。 <br />\n<br />\n另外，25款午餐肉樣本驗出的鈉含量差異大，其中以「759阿信屋」午餐豬肉最鹹，每100克含1180毫克鈉，與鈉含量最低的「古龍」午餐肉(每100克含517毫克)相差超過一倍。根據世衞建議，一般成年人每日的鈉攝取量應少於2000毫克，以鈉含量最高的「759阿信屋」午餐豬肉計算，進食半罐已超出建議限值。 <br />\n<br />\n消委會測試亦發現，樣本的鈉含量與產品標籤不符，6款午餐肉樣本驗出量較標示高，差異最大的是「長城牌」火腿豬肉(金龍)樣本，其檢出量比標示量高25%。至於腸仔樣本方面，「Princes」Hot Dogs 8's樣本的營養標籤資料甚至出錯，檢出的鈉含量(每100克含851毫克)較標示量(每100克含1.5毫克)高出560倍。 <br />\n<br />\n另外，標榜「較低鈉」的午餐肉亦非如聲稱，有3款午餐肉樣本鈉含量低於聲稱，消委會又發現部分生產商會在肉類罐頭食物加入亞硝酸鈉，以防止孳生細菌。有6個午餐肉和3個腸仔樣本驗出含亞硝酸鈉。 <br />\n<br />\n消委會指，午餐肉和腸仔是港式早餐常見的搭配，假設食用兩片午餐肉和兩條腸仔，以驗出最高鈉含量的樣本作參考，配以麵包或即食麵，即吃一個早餐便有機會超出每日攝入限量。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170615/mobile/bkn-20170615100007641-0615_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170615%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170615100007641-0615_00822_001.html&d=z9kzH8MKTQWsgj0QUwzsjC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=126faada\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170615/mobile/bkn-20170615100007641-0615_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f1cee398b67479cee1a792496ef3945173d6e003","tid":284431,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T02:41:22.000Z","msg":"另有1款腸仔樣本的鈉含量比所標示的高出560多倍<br />\n<br />\n一條大約200鈉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 560倍 112000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"063c69b58dd9f43b74d523aebc1eca2b15a48e44","tid":284431,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T02:42:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>支那製造</blockquote><br />\n三花, 泡菜牌牛餐肉唔好得好多<br />\n只係呢隻支那牌子行內連狗都唔屌</blockquote><br />\n加工罐頭肉實係咁架啦<br />\n行內睇你咩行啦 茶記理撚得你咩 最緊要平</blockquote><br />\n茶記d牛餐肉邊有咁細罐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n梅林牌都有大罐裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e7d342f7fa2ccdfff496ce5784bb7fea5f071c4","tid":284431,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T02:42:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>另有1款腸仔樣本的鈉含量比所標示的高出560多倍<br />\n<br />\n一條大約200鈉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 560倍 112000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個腎冇喇個腎冇喇"},{"pid":"76b0ce9b51bfcf5786bf8bca11eea2f707ac07e9","tid":284431,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T02:51:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>另有1款腸仔樣本的鈉含量比所標示的高出560多倍<br />\n<br />\n一條大約200鈉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 560倍 112000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />標1.5, 驗800幾"}]}